        "llm_details": {
          "1a_score": 5,
          "1a_reason": "Instrument references are frequent (bass intro, drum entry, guitar chunking, cowbell hits, DJ scratch, congas, riser), and some are tied to specific counts (e.g., cowbell at 36/38, DJ scratch at 41). However, most correspondences remain macro-level (section features) rather than beat-level mapping to snare 2&4/hi-hat/kick patterns, and several claims (e.g., “drum syncopation” in Verse 15-16) are not anchored to explicit instrument hits.",
